msgstr "次断线/5分钟"

msgid "occasional drops"
msgstr "偶发断线"

msgid "link stable"
msgstr "链路稳定"

msgid "24h"
msgstr "24小时"

msgid "last"
msgstr "最近"

msgid "Details / history ›"
msgstr "详情 / 历史 ›"

msgid "Port is unstable (flapping)"
msgstr "端口不稳定（抖动中）"

msgid "Port is administratively disabled"
msgstr "端口已被管理员禁用"

msgid "Port is disconnected – cable unplugged or remote side down"
msgstr "端口已断开 – 网线未插或对端已关闭"

msgid "Port is active"
msgstr "端口已连接"

msgid "no critical errors"
msgstr "无严重错误"

msgid "Reset counters and history"
msgstr "重置计数器和历史"

msgid "This action will clear the flap history and save the current error counter values as a new baseline. Values will restart from zero."
msgstr "此操作将清除抖动历史并将当前错误计数器值保存为新基准。计数将从零重新开始。"

msgid "Continue?"
msgstr "是否继续？"

msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "取消"

msgid "Counters have been reset. Table refreshed."
msgstr "计数器已重置，表格已刷新。"

msgid "Reset failed"
msgstr "重置失败"

msgid "Reset"
msgstr "重置"

msgid "Reset error counters and flap history"
msgstr "重置错误计数器和抖动历史"

msgid "No events yet (history is cleared on restart)."
msgstr "暂无事件（重启后历史记录会被清除）。"

msgid "UP"
msgstr "上线"

msgid "DOWN"
msgstr "下线"

msgid "Counter"
msgstr "计数器"

msgid "Total"
msgstr "累计"

msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

msgid "disabled"
msgstr "已禁用"

msgid "disconnected"
msgstr "已断开"

msgid "active"
msgstr "已连接"

msgid "none yet"
msgstr "暂无"

msgid "Stability"
msgstr "稳定性"

msgid "Flaps"
msgstr "抖动次数"

msgid "Last event"
msgstr "最近事件"

msgid "Loading…"
msgstr "加载中…"

msgid "Event history"
msgstr "事件历史"

msgid "Critical error counters (RX)"
msgstr "严重错误计数器（RX）"

msgid "Critical error counters (TX)"
msgstr "严重错误计数器（TX）"

msgid "Informational counters"
msgstr "信息性计数器"

msgid "These counters typically grow without issues – e.g. LLDP/CDP/IPv6 ND. Do not use them to assess port health."
msgstr "这些计数器在正常情况下也会增长（如 LLDP/CDP/IPv6 ND），请勿用于评估端口健康状态。"

msgid "Close"
msgstr "关闭"

msgid "Port diagnostics"
msgstr "端口诊断"

msgid "Failed to load events"
msgstr "加载事件失败"

msgid "Sum of all RX errors (CRC, frame, fifo, length, …). If growing, there is a HW/cabling problem."
msgstr "所有 RX 错误的汇总（CRC、帧、FIFO、长度等）。若持续增长，说明存在硬件或线缆问题。"

msgid "Bad frame checksum. Typically bad cable, EMI interference, faulty connector or NIC."
msgstr "帧校验和错误。通常由线缆质量差、电磁干扰、接头故障或网卡问题引起。"

msgid "Frame misalignment. Usually bad cable, faulty NIC or duplex mismatch."
msgstr "帧对齐错误。通常由线缆质量差、网卡故障或双工不匹配引起。"

msgid "NIC FIFO buffer overflow. CPU or bus cannot keep up with incoming traffic."
msgstr "网卡 FIFO 缓冲区溢出。CPU 或总线处理速度跟不上入站流量。"

msgid "RX ring buffer overflow in driver. Same cause as rx_fifo, different layer."
msgstr "驱动层 RX 环形缓冲区溢出。原因与 rx_fifo 相同，但发生在不同层次。"

msgid "Packet received physically but Linux kernel dropped it before passing to the network stack (no registered protocol handler)."
msgstr "物理层已收到数据包，但 Linux 内核在传递到网络栈前将其丢弃（无对应协议处理器）。"

msgid "Most common causes:"
msgstr "最常见原因："

msgid "LLDP (0x88CC) from managed switch – every 30 s"
msgstr "来自托管交换机的 LLDP (0x88CC) – 每 30 秒一次"

msgid "STP/RSTP BPDU from switch"
msgstr "来自交换机的 STP/RSTP BPDU"

msgid "IPv6 ND/RA without active IPv6 listener"
msgstr "无活跃 IPv6 监听器时收到的 IPv6 ND/RA"

msgid "Packets with VLAN tag the interface cannot decode"
msgstr "接口无法解码的 VLAN 标签数据包"

msgid "Slow growth (1–5/min) on a port connected to a managed switch is NORMAL. Consider action only when growth > 50/min or sudden spike."
msgstr "连接到托管交换机的端口缓慢增长（1–5/分钟）属于正常现象。仅当增速超过 50/分钟或出现突然飙升时才需处理。"

msgid "Sum of all TX errors. If growing, there is a problem on the link or NIC."
msgstr "所有 TX 错误的汇总。若持续增长，说明链路或网卡存在问题。"

msgid "Loss of carrier during transmission. Bad cable, poor connection or sudden link drops."
msgstr "发送期间丢失载波信号。通常由线缆质量差、连接不良或链路突然中断引起。"

msgid "Transmission aborted – usually after reaching repeated collision limit. Indicates congested or half-duplex segment."
msgstr "发送中止 – 通常是达到重复碰撞次数上限。表明网段拥塞或处于半双工模式。"

msgid "NIC TX FIFO buffer overflow."
msgstr "网卡 TX FIFO 缓冲区溢出。"

msgid "Line collisions. Normal on half-duplex. On full-duplex indicates duplex mismatch and a serious problem."
msgstr "线路碰撞。半双工模式下属正常，全双工模式下表明双工不匹配，是严重问题。"

msgid "Outgoing packet was not sent and kernel dropped it before NIC."
msgstr "出站数据包未发送，内核在到达网卡之前将其丢弃。"

msgid "Full egress queue at shaper / QoS (htb, tbf, cake)"
msgstr "整形器/QoS（htb、tbf、cake）出站队列已满"

msgid "No route – missing route to destination"
msgstr "无路由 – 缺少到目标的路由"

msgid "Interface in admin down during transmission"
msgstr "发送期间接口处于管理禁用状态"

msgid "Traffic shaping limit or rate-limit on NIC"
msgstr "流量整形限制或网卡速率限制"

msgid "Sent multicast without registered listeners"
msgstr "发送了无接收者注册的多播包"

msgid "Under normal operation this value should stay 0 or grow very slowly. A sudden spike indicates congestion or misconfigured QoS."
msgstr "正常运行时此值应保持为 0 或增长极缓慢。突然飙升表明网络拥塞或 QoS 配置有误。"

msgid "Show error counters for RX/TX columns"
msgstr "在 RX/TX 列显示错误计数器"

msgid "Instability threshold (flap count per 5 minutes)"
msgstr "不稳定阈值（每5分钟抖动次数）"

msgid "When this value is exceeded the port is marked as UNSTABLE."
msgstr "超过此值时端口将被标记为不稳定。"

msgid "(incoming packets)"
msgstr "（入站数据包）"

msgid "(outgoing packets)"
msgstr "（出站数据包）"

msgid "Δ refresh"
msgstr "Δ 刷新间隔"

msgid "Cisco CDP / HP FDP / ExtremeNetworks EDP / Nortel SONMP"
msgstr "Cisco CDP / HP FDP / ExtremeNetworks EDP / Nortel SONMP"

msgid "MikroTik MNDP (UDP/5678 broadcast)"
msgstr "MikroTik MNDP (UDP/5678 广播)"
